    <h3>Requirements</h3>
    <p>The Program will be <strong>Monday, June 4th through Thursday, June 28th</strong>. Students are expected to work from <strong>1pm-6pm, M-Th</strong>, and must be able to attend each session in its entirety. Department-specific training programs will occur on different dates, and will have different time requirements.</p>
    <p>Students must be in good standing with the University, and plan to be enrolled at UT for at least two semesters after the summer program.</p>
    <p>Students that wish to learn web development or mobile development must have their own laptop.</p>
    <p>There may be some small fees to access a portion of the required online trainings.</p>
